#+begin_quote

Fetch high-quality wallpapers from this amazing site: [[https://wallpaperswide.com/][WallpapersWide.com - Free
4K & 8K UltraHD Desktop Backgound Wallpapers]].

All the image data will be used only for particular research purposes.

#+end_quote

* Install dependencies

#+begin_src sh
brew install wget
#+end_src

#+begin_src sh
cargo install htmlq
#+end_src

* Usage

#+begin_src sh
mkdir -p downloads
. ./get-walls.sh
#+end_src
